title: Basaigiri nwng angni
lyrics:
Basaigiri nwng angni
Rwikhagiri nwng angni-2
Swmw nangtao Fwrbu nwngni onnai -2
(A)
Angni ayen barsinnai takwi nwngw
Jokhom jabai
Angni inai maonaini takwisw nwngw 
Bukrup jabai-2
(B)
Krushni sayao alaijablabw nwng ankhou
 Nimaha hwbai
Nwngw banso haywi dukhu swinanwibw
Ankhou basai bai-2
